==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Orthographize
<hw>Or*thog"ra*phize</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To spell
correctly or according to usage; to correct in regard to
spelling.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>In the</qex> coalesced into <qex>ith</qex>, which modern
reaction has <qex>orthographized</qex> to <qex>i' th'</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Earle.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Orthography</ent>⟦br⟧
